name: CI Morningstar Canada Momentum Index ETF
longDescription: The fund has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the Morningstar Canada Target Momentum Index (the Index), net of expenses. The ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the Morningstar Canada Target Momentum Index (the Index), net of expenses. The ETF invests in equity securities of the largest and most liquid Canadian issuers based on proprietary research generated by Morningstar, and is designed to provide diversified exposure to Canadian issuers which have demonstrated, among other things, positive momentum in earnings and price.
